reviewText: You must have a perfect, slim and muscular body for the practices. It is a delight to watch.
Wonderful, advanced, flowing Vinyasa Yoga..beautiful examples with clear instructions on how to create the postures. I highly praise this Tantric sequence
Hier "nur" drei sterne, hat aber dennoch gefallen. Kann dennoch "aufregender" gefilmt werden. Die Kameraeinstellungen werden den Aktuerinnen nicht ganz gerecht.
A very good DVD, well produced, excellent model and poses, generous nudity (although more closeups and more intimate poses would've been better).  I can recommend this disc.
